The incredibly sexy Julie (Scarlet Salem, ''Strip Club Slasher'') and Nick (Donny Versiga, ''Sinister'') are on a road trip which derails after they become involved in a series of gruesome murders committed by what seems to be a large ape-like creature (Mr. Sasquatch). Will either of them survive to learn the secret of Mr. Sasquatch? ''Shriek of the Sasquatch'' comes in the tradition of retro hits such as ''Grindhouse'' and is packed with drive in-style fun from cult director Steve Sessions.

It's 1979 and gorgeous babe Julie (Scarlet Salem, "Strip Club Slasher") and Nick (Donny Versiga) are on a road trip which puts them unwittingly on a collision course with Mr. Sasquatch. Will either of them survive to learn the secret of Mr. Sasquatch? Pseudo-retro drive-in fun, complete with film damage. Filmed in 2010.
